WEBVTT

00:53.247 --> 00:54.947
<b>Guess I'll head to work.</b>

01:16.517 --> 01:20.487
<b><i>I can make 60,000 a month cutting trees.</i></b>

01:20.977 --> 01:25.737
<b><i>For the kidney, I got 1,200,000.</i></b>

01:26.307 --> 01:29.487
<b><i>For my right eye, 300,000.</i></b>

01:30.097 --> 01:32.747
<b><i>And for one of my balls...</i></b>

01:33.147 --> 01:35.147
<b><i>How much did I get for it, again?</i></b>

01:35.147 --> 01:37.327
<b><i>I don't think it was even 100,000.</i></b>

01:40.387 --> 01:42.877
<b><i>And I'm still in debt...</i></b>

01:43.597 --> 01:45.877
<b><i>to the tune of 38,040,000.</i></b>

01:50.007 --> 01:53.187
<b>I know, Pochita.</b>

01:53.187 --> 01:55.267
<b>Let's go kill one.</b>

01:55.997 --> 02:00.737
<b>I can make around 300,000 from killing just one devil.</b>

02:04.427 --> 02:07.737
<b>Yup, nothing beats being a devil hunter.</b>

02:22.667 --> 02:25.257
<b>This is a tomato devil.</b>

02:25.717 --> 02:28.817
<b>It can come back from its seeds, 
so you should burn it.</b>

02:28.817 --> 02:31.007
<b>Good work, Denji.</b>

02:31.377 --> 02:35.537
<b>This one's corpse will fetch a hefty sum on the black market.</b>

02:35.537 --> 02:37.517
<b>I'll give you 400,000.</b>

02:37.517 --> 02:38.417
<b>Thanks!</b>

02:38.417 --> 02:41.667
<b>Minus your loan repayments and interest, that's 170,000.</b>

02:41.667 --> 02:49.147
<b>Then after accounting for the brokerage fee, 
admin fee, overheads, and so on...</b>

02:49.907 --> 02:51.647
<b>I'm left with 70,000.</b>

02:51.657 --> 02:58.917
Sakae

02:51.657 --> 02:58.917
Real

02:51.657 --> 02:58.917
