02:51.657 --> 02:58.917
tazaki s

02:52.227 --> 02:58.917
<b>And after paying the water bill and some of my other debts...</b>

02:58.917 --> 03:01.917


02:59.497 --> 03:00.907
<b>Would you look at that?</b>

03:01.607 --> 03:04.407
<b>Only 1,800 yen left.</b>

03:01.917 --> 03:04.917


03:04.417 --> 03:11.177
